      "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* Add modular agent skills framework by @dpark01 in https://github.com/broadinstitute/viral-ngs/pull/1054\r\n* Fix tag cleanup to prevent cascade deletion of shared-digest images by @dpark01 in https://github.com/broadinstitute/viral-ngs/pull/1055\r\n* Bump pyopenssl conda pin to >=26.0.0 by @dpark01 in https://github.com/broadinstitute/viral-ngs/pull/1056\r\n* Enforce Trivy severity filter on SARIF output and fail CI on findings by @dpark01 in https://github.com/broadinstitute/viral-ngs/pull/1057\r\n* Fix CVE-2026-33210: upgrade Ruby json gem in assemble, phylo, and mega images by @dpark01 in https://github.com/broadinstitute/viral-ngs/pull/1058\r\n* Add rasusa-based coverage normalization for assembly polishing by @dpark01 in https://github.com/broadinstitute/viral-ngs/pull/1059\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/broadinstitute/viral-ngs/compare/v3.0.10...v3.0.11",
